==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: bú shì yuān jiā bú jù tóu
===Proverb===
'''[[不]][[是]][[冤]][[家]][[不]][[聚]][[頭]]'''
# [Idiom] if you were not destined to be lovers, you would not be together.
